Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,真是疯了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那小子可不是一般的小鬼头
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定…赢得了他…
